            <thetext>The meta data for the tests that is retreived with TestLoader.getTestDescriptions() should include optional text that describes tests or whole test classes.

This information could be provided to the user through e.g. tooltip-like popups when the cursor hoovers over the respective node in the tree view.

The description could be taken from the test JavaScript source files, in the form of standard jsdoc docstrings on classes and methods.

The JSON-type metadata returned by TestLoader.getTestDescription() could be extended with a &#39;desc&#39; keyword to capture these descriptive texts.</thetext>
